## 📌 What Is This File?

`main.py` is the **brain of the entire game**. It does 4 big jobs:
1. Sets up the window and game loop
2. Draws all shared visuals (space background, player character, buttons)
3. Manages the menus (Home, Costume Picker, Level Select)
4. Handles the save/unlock system

Every level file (`Level1.py` to `Level10.py`) **imports from this file** to use the shared drawing tools and save system.

