## ⚙️ DEV MODE Toggle

```python
DEVELOPER_MODE = False  # True = all levels unlocked (for testing)
```

**Why I built this:**
- While building the game, I needed to jump to any level instantly without playing through all previous ones
- Setting `DEVELOPER_MODE = True` skips all unlock gates
- Setting it back to `False` restores normal locked progression for players
- A small orange badge appears on screen so I always know which mode I'm in

