## 🎭 costume_menu()

- Displays all 9 costumes in a grid
- Each box shows a live preview of that costume using `draw_player()`
- Currently selected costume gets a yellow border
- Clicking a costume sets `current_costume` (a global variable) and returns
- Uses `divmod(i, cols)` to calculate grid row and column positions automatically

